column5: This is me just now. There are things you say that you can never take back
help me is exactly what I have been thinking all day. Just need to focus on school I've been too lazy too sleepy too horny lonely to do shit
Soo how old is your kid
What does swipe swipe mean if I can ask

It's an extremely condescending experience, you tell them your deepest secrets and they wipe their ass with it and eventually tell you to DO things "to improve" and when you don't you get blamed for it but you ALREADY know it's your fault that you don't DO these things.

They couldn't pay me $100 per session to return and scar me even more than they already have.
